  "informal_statement": "For all reals a and b, (a+b)² ≤ 2(a²+b²) (a QM-AM / power-mean bound).",
  "informal_proof_idea": "2(a²+b²) - (a+b)² = (a-b)² ≥ 0. nlinarith with the square hint.",
  "formal_statement_pp": "theorem qm_am_bound (a b : ℝ) : (a + b) ^ 2 ≤ 2 * (a ^ 2 + b ^ 2)",
